comment: Domestic violence is almost always a long term pattern of behavior, and rarely as is alleged by Heard.  My ex-wife was a domestic violence counselor and educator. None of his friends and past partners have affirmed an abusive personality pattern.  I hope the evidence from the police officers who responded to the abuse call, their sworn statements and the body camera video will yield more factual information. Mr. Depp has suffered a great deal of financial loss, career repercussions and smeared reputation.  Personally, I find Johnny Deep a good human being. God bless him. May we pray for and imagine a time in the near future when he is exonerated. May the truth come out asap.

comment:
What I don't understand is why people would say this person did not beat his wife, or was not a rapist or a so-and-so. It is dangerous when we don't have factual evidence to support what we believe happened. We just don't know because we weren't there. I think both of them are insane and toxic, and should be going to therapy and going to AAA meetings. They should be made an example. And both of them are making a huge damage and disservice to people who are victims of domestic violence and get killed every year.

"Anyone can be a victim of domestic violence. There is NO "typical victim." Victims of domestic violence comes from all walks of life, varying age groups, all backgrounds, all communities, all education levels, all economic levels, all cultures, all ethnicities, all religions, all abilities, and all lifestyles. 


Victims of domestic violence do not bring violence upon themselves, they do not always lack self-confidence, nor are they just as abusive as the abuser. Violence in relationships occurs when one person feels entitled to power and control over their partner and chooses to use abuse to gain and maintain that control. In relationships where domestic violence exists, violence is not equal. Even if the victim fights back or instigates violence in an effort to diffuse a situation. There is always one person who is the primary, constant source of power, control, and abuse in the relationship" 

Source
https://www.ncadv.org/statistics

comment:
Amber Heard has been proven with evidence time and time again how much she lies. Making her word mean nothing. The fact that people still believe her is astounding. Perhaps they don't want to admit to being wrong, or that a woman can be abusive.

Lets start with her character
-Amber Heard gave her dog an Arab name then would call them her 'little terrorist'. She took a photo of a Black man, mocking him with 'Stereotypes are fun'. She sent a text using the 'N word'. She visited a Holy Mosque for a photoshoot with her tits on full display through her sheer shirt and lack of bra, and hair not tied back, as well getting a photo where you can see a man praying in the background (which is illegal).

-Being investigated for Perjury by Australia (and possibly the LAPD)

-AH has a prior arrest for Domestic Violence against her then Wife/Girlfriend, and claimed the Police officer who arrested her only did so because they were Homophobic. The Police officer in question being a proud Lesbian.

-She is a drug and alcohol abuser; I only mention this since people love to use that against Mr. Depp despite the fact Amber Heard is a Drug addict and drinker herself.

-AH Claimed JD held her little dog out a car window and she was terrified he'd drop them. However there is video footage that SHE took herself, where she is the one holding the tiny teacup terrier out of the window of the moving car while filming and laughing.

-Is seen on Elevator video taking multiple men up to Mr. Depp's penthouse while the two were still married and Mr. Depp wasn't around due to filming. We also have video of her going into an elevator and throwing food out onto the floor without concern about those who'd have to clean up after her. 

-She secretly records her 'friends', (Proof: in the UK trial a recording was used in which she'd recorded of a friend without their knowledge as they spoke about JD's lawyers)

Moving on to the Case and Evidence.
-AH's photos of 'injuries', not only show they move around her face, but they 'run' down her cheeks when she has a couple tears. She is on TV and has photoshoots showing not a single injury whatsoever when she is suppose to be sporting a broken nose, 2 black eyes, split lips, bruised ribs and so on.

-Besides her faked photos her only evidence against Mr. Depp is her word, and that of her close friends who were living Rent free in the Penthouses. The Video of Mr. Depp hitting cupboards, after he'd lost a great deal of money and Amber is seen smirking at the end. And the graphic Text between Mr. Depp and a friend where he vented about the person abusing him and ended it stating her could never hurt her.

-Despite all the graphic injuries she claims, she has been no medial records at all and her only photos is a red spot on her cheek. She took photos of writing all over mirrors, but never of the injuries she claimed to have at that time. Feet and Arms sliced open on glass, strangulation marks, bruises, etc. She is also practicing ballet a few weeks later with no scars on the feet. A Broken nose often needs medical attention to heal correctly, something you'd expect an actress/Model to seek. Yet again, no medical records to be found. Not to mention she claimed Mr. Depp hit her in the back of the head multiple times while wearing his heavy rings. Yet no indication of head trauma or the concussion she surely would have suffered.

-She blatantly lied for 4 or more years over donating money to Dying Children and DV survivors. She used this lie to prove she is no gold digger, she had no motive, she is a generous and giving person. Yet when truth comes out she never donated a dime she immediately blamed Mr. Depp, despite the face she had the full amount months before she was ever sued and needed to pay for legal fees. Then claims she 'pledged the money over 10 years', despite being on TV, telling the Media, and in Court documents clearly stating she had donated the entire amount.

-She changes her stories multiple times to adapt to evidence; Her stories all contained very highly detailed things of little to no importance, can recall exactly what rooms their fights had them moving between. But then can't remember the simplest of details, or even how she gets out of situations like being pinned faced down on a bed. Some Details either don't even make sense or are completely wrong. Such as Mr. Depp being able to kick a plane chair at her, chairs that are bolted to the floor, or how she claimed 'Blood sprayed across the Smeg Fridge' when the Smeg wasn't bought until a few months later.

-She is accused of stealing another woman's sexual assault story. 

-Bodycam footage proves no damage at the penthouse. Even if they cleaned up the glass everything else was in place. Nothing was broken. There was no 'gigantic' wine stains across the walls.

-'Poopgate', she blamed her tiny Teacup Terrier on the human sized faecal matter on the bed that the dog likely needs help even getting on. 

-She is on voice recording to admitting to hitting Mr. Depp, throwing things at him Gaslighting, Insulting him, Drugging him, and saying she can't promise she won't get angry again. All the while complaining that Mr. Depp always 'Splits' from fights.

-Police, Nurse, Former Assistances, and a Makeup Artist have all testified against Amber Heard. From confirming they have not see her with injuries, to a story about how she used her assistants child without constant for some paparazzi photos.

-Amber Heard claimed that her Op-Ed was never about Mr. Depp. She said UNDER OATH, it had nothing to do with Mr. Depp. Yet here we are with emails back and forth between her and the ACLU about writing the article, being careful not to directly mention Mr. Depp, getting lawyers to check it over to make sure its safe, to 'skirt around' mention of her marriage.


I could in fact go one, but this is long enough.
TL/DR: Amber Heard is scum who'd using dying children and lies about everything. She has no evidence other than her word, while there is a mountain of evidence disproving her claims at every single turn.
